title: Snupps - Collect Organize Share
description:
Join two million people who organize and connect around the stuff they own and love.
Whatever you are into: streetwear, comics, fashion, collectibles or anything else, Snupps lets you ->
- Organize your collections on virtual shelves (private or public)
- Connect and chat with people who share your passions
- Discover trends and be inspired
- Join groups related to your interests
- Manage personal inventory and spending
- Create special moments and tag your favorite stuff / friends
- Share to Facebook, Instagram, Twitter and WhatsApp
- Buy and Sell
See you on Snupps!
